AXI4 Examples Overview

This directory contains examples that use the AXI4 BFM from the Mentor Verification IP Altera Edition.

* axi4_use_model_sv - A SystemVerilog example to demonstrate the Master, Slave and Monitor APIs.
* axi4_use_model_vhd - A VHDL example to demonstrate the Master, Slave and Monitor APIs.

Each example directory contains the following files

* top.*                   - the top-level module for the test.
* master_test_program.*   - the master test stimulus.
* slave_test_program.*    - the slave test stimulus.
* monitor_test_program.*  - the protocol traffic monitor.
* script.do               - the run script.

To run any example, execute the following command on a commnd prompt

> cd axi4_use_model_sv
> vsim -do script.do -mvchome ../../../common
> run 2000 ns

This will load and run the self-checking test.
